00:12.946 --> 00:14.248
LUCIOUS:
I don't care how many of us

00:14.282 --> 00:15.383
you've locked behind bars.

00:15.416 --> 00:16.584
You ain't never
gonna be nothing

00:16.617 --> 00:18.419
but a black bitch
in cheap shoes.

00:18.452 --> 00:20.688
COOKIE: In partnership
with Mimi Whiteman,

00:20.721 --> 00:22.990
we have taken a controlling
interest in Empire.

00:23.023 --> 00:24.558
Sorry, brother,
it's just business.

00:24.592 --> 00:25.659
Yeah, it's just business.

00:25.693 --> 00:28.196
Right, Mimi?
Lucious Lyon is Empire.

00:28.229 --> 00:29.997
Without him,
the company is nothing.

00:30.030 --> 00:32.366
I'm gonna bury
your album, Hakeem.

00:32.400 --> 00:34.668
Get out of my father's house.
You betrayed him.

00:34.702 --> 00:37.371
