now it's gone.

00:48.382 --> 00:49.450
Stop complainin'.

00:49.483 --> 00:51.419
We don't need this place.

00:51.452 --> 00:52.920
We can start our own company.

00:52.953 --> 00:55.022
I woke up this morning thinking

00:55.055 --> 00:57.125
why don't we do
what the hell I said?

00:57.158 --> 00:58.626
We gonna start
our own company.

00:58.659 --> 00:59.927
ANDRE:
It'll never work, Mom.

00:59.960 --> 01:01.028
The business has
changed completely

01:01.061 --> 01:02.029
since you and
Dad started out.

01:02.062 --> 01:03.697
This could work.

01:03.731 --> 01:05.099
We just need a dope name.

01:05.133 --> 01:06.800
We've got Hakeem.

01:06.834 --> 01:09.403
All he has to do is record
one more song for his album.

01:09.437 --> 01:11.139
Empire will never
let us have that album.

01:11.172 --> 01:12.406
You heard Jamal.
He's going to bury it.

01:12.440 --> 01:13.407
Let me deal with Jamal.

01:13.441 --> 01:14.542
All right, bye.

01:14.575 --> 01:16.544
Look, Mom, we need
to go after Royale T,

01:16.577 --> 01:18.379
Ratzo and Tiana.

01:18.412 --> 01:19.647
