01:19.680 --> 01:20.881
She's down with us.

01:20.914 --> 01:22.816
We just gotta get you
back into the studio.

01:22.850 --> 01:25.753
Okay, Mom, I'm so much more
than just a rapper.

01:25.786 --> 01:28.222
Let me develop my own artists.

01:28.256 --> 01:29.923
I bet Anika can get V.

01:29.957 --> 01:31.559
No! No.
Anika's out.

01:31.592 --> 01:33.227
I don't want to see
her lying face,

01:33.261 --> 01:34.562
you understand me, Keem?

01:34.595 --> 01:35.663
I told V we'd get
straight to work

01:35.696 --> 01:36.764
recording her
new single, so...

01:36.797 --> 01:38.299
Are you sure
Cookie wants me?

01:38.332 --> 01:39.967
Yeah, she definitely
wants you.

01:40.000 --> 01:41.235
Pride of the Lyons is wack.

01:41.269 --> 01:42.303
It's a terrible name.

01:42.336 --> 01:43.771
Did you tell Mom
you talked to Anika?

01:43.804 --> 01:45.806
Man, she don't want
nothing to do with her,

01:45.839 --> 01:48.108
Thank you.
but I told Anika
to come anyway.

01:48.142 --> 01:50.811
Nah, I like Pride
of the Lyons better.

01:50.844 --> 01:52.946
Look, we can call it
whatever you want, baby,

01:52.980 --> 01:54.582
as long as you in it with me.

01:54.615 --> 01:56.016
I think you should
reconsider Anika.

01:56.049 --> 01:57.585
She's one of the top
A&Rs in the business.

01:57.618 --> 02:00.921
I don't care how good she is,
I don't trust her ass.

02:00.954 --> 02:02.956
I just need you
with me on this, baby.

02:02.990 --> 02:04.325
I'm thinking about it, Ma.

02:04.358 --> 02:05.793
Just give me
a second to breathe.

02:07.795 --> 02:09.830
I actually think it could work.

02:09.863 --> 02:11.932
(phone line ringing)

02:11.965 --> 02:12.933
COOKIE: Hello?

02:12.966 --> 02:14.502
Hey, Ma, I want to start

02:14.535 --> 02:15.769
a girl group
like Destiny's Child.

02:15.803 --> 02:17.371
That's a great idea, Keem.

02:17.405 --> 02:19.640
Look, I think I got
a space for us to rent

02:19.673 --> 02:21.108
if Andre can
cut us a deal.

02:21.141 --> 02:22.109
Is Andre in?

02:22.142 --> 02:23.711
Well, he's gonna be.

02:23.744 --> 02:25.713
Look, just meet me at
Ghetto Ass Studio tomorrow.

02:25.746 --> 02:28.449
She's kidding, right?

02:28.482 --> 02:30.851
Forget Lyon's Den,
let's just call it The Pigsty.

02:30.884 --> 02:31.852
Man, we need a name
like Em...

02:31.885 --> 02:32.853
Forget the name, okay?

02:32.886 --> 02:34.355
The name is beside the point.

02:34.388 --> 02:36.690
You ain't born with your name.
You grow into it.

02:36.724 --> 02:39.627
Yeah, when we started Empire,
we wasn't no Empire.

02:39.660 --> 02:42.363
