06:03.363 --> 06:05.232
WOMAN:
Wow.

06:06.266 --> 06:08.669
That was amazing.

06:08.702 --> 06:10.237
Thank you so much.
Thank you.

06:10.270 --> 06:12.005
Looking forward to
speaking to you.

06:12.039 --> 06:13.607
Oh, looking forward
to speaking to you, as well.

06:13.641 --> 06:15.509
I'm so happy you even
want to talk to me.

06:15.543 --> 06:16.510
Oh, of course.

06:16.544 --> 06:18.045
Thank you.
Who wouldn't?

06:18.078 --> 06:19.046
Okay.
MAN: Rolling!

06:19.079 --> 06:21.214
Jamal Lyon.
Yes.

06:21.248 --> 06:23.517
Wow, look at you!
(chuckles)

06:23.551 --> 06:25.252
Thank you for
that incredible song.

06:25.285 --> 06:27.855
Thank you.
And for
inviting us into

06:27.888 --> 06:29.189
your gorgeous home.
Of course.

06:29.222 --> 06:30.924
Any time. Yeah.
We're so lucky

06:30.958 --> 06:32.259
to have you here on
Spilling the Tea.

06:32.292 --> 06:34.094
As you can see from our P.A.

06:34.127 --> 06:36.363
over there, who has
a little crush on you,

06:36.396 --> 06:38.899
