Men, as well,

06:49.242 --> 06:50.711
by the way.
(laughs)

06:50.744 --> 06:52.446
It's great.
I mean, we-we love,

06:52.480 --> 06:53.714
we love everybody.
It's beautiful.

06:53.747 --> 06:55.415
It must be tough
on relationships,

06:55.449 --> 06:56.950
though, right?
No, I don't think so.

06:56.984 --> 06:59.152
Um, if, uh,
if the relationship is solid.

06:59.186 --> 07:00.888
I don't...
It doesn't
cause jealousy?

07:00.921 --> 07:02.556
No, I don't... No.

07:02.590 --> 07:03.924
SHARON:
His name is Michael.

07:03.957 --> 07:06.093
He's a little shy,
but trust me, ladies,

07:06.126 --> 07:07.961
he is adorable.

07:07.995 --> 07:10.297
Plus, he cooked us
the most amazing meal

07:10.330 --> 07:12.466
while we were setting up.
But still,

07:12.500 --> 07:13.734
you know you're a lucky
guy, Michael, right?

07:13.767 --> 07:14.802
Yeah.
JAMAL:
Nah.

07:14.835 --> 07:16.003
No, no, I'm the lucky one.

07:16.036 --> 07:17.104
So, Jamal,

07:17.137 --> 07:19.106
