any time soon?

07:21.441 --> 07:23.143
You know we're all
waiting for it.

07:23.176 --> 07:25.479
Uh, I don't know about "soon."

07:25.513 --> 07:28.315
Uh... I am
creating music.

07:28.348 --> 07:29.817
You know, it's my everything,

07:29.850 --> 07:31.985
and, you know,
just been a little...

07:32.019 --> 07:33.153
I've been a little busy.

07:33.186 --> 07:34.154
You've been a little busy,

07:34.187 --> 07:35.623
