hard for you.

07:41.361 --> 07:43.764
Yeah. Uh, I can't say
too much about it,

07:43.797 --> 07:45.332
but, you know, I'm...

07:45.365 --> 07:47.167
just that I'm working
on my music,

07:47.200 --> 07:49.837
a-as always, and making sure

07:49.870 --> 07:51.839
that I continue to make smart

07:51.872 --> 07:53.974
