08:08.088 --> 08:09.657
Cookie Lyon.
We spoke on the phone, Sharon.

08:09.690 --> 08:10.858
Good to see you.

08:10.891 --> 08:12.560
Mm-hmm.
Uh-huh. Yeah, Mom.

08:12.593 --> 08:14.361
Let's go. Come on.

08:15.829 --> 08:18.331
I am trying to do an interview,
in case you didn't notice.

08:18.365 --> 08:19.800
In case you have not noticed,

08:19.833 --> 08:21.301
I set up that interview.

08:21.334 --> 08:22.570
I have to get to the lawyer
after this,

08:22.603 --> 08:23.971
to try to get my father
out of jail,

08:24.004 --> 08:25.172
since you all bailed on him,

08:25.205 --> 08:26.807
so can we make this quick?
Please?

08:26.840 --> 08:29.376
Look, I need to talk
to you about Hakeem.

08:29.409 --> 08:30.544
Oh. Little baby traitor.

08:30.578 --> 08:33.513
He didn't do anything
to hurt you, Jamal.

08:33.547 --> 08:35.482
He was hurt. By Lucious.

08:35.515 --> 08:37.551
And I know you know
what that feels like.

08:42.422 --> 08:44.992
I need you to give Hakeem
his album back.

08:45.025 --> 08:47.027
Why would I do that?

08:47.060 --> 08:49.162
(sighs)

08:49.196 --> 08:50.397
Jamal, you already won.

08:50.430 --> 08:54.201
You run the Empire.

08:54.234 --> 08:56.236
All Hakeem's got is his music.

08:58.305 --> 09:01.008
I know you.

09:01.041 --> 09:05.112
See, Lucious is trying
to make you like him, but...

09:05.145 --> 09:07.180
you ain't him.
(chuckles)

09:07.214 --> 09:10.350
