walk me to these elevators.

09:10.383 --> 09:12.853
Show these cameras how good
you're being to your mom.

09:12.886 --> 09:14.287
It's Mom.
Can't say nothing to Mom.

09:14.321 --> 09:15.956
I'm sorry for
the interruption.

09:15.989 --> 09:17.691
Sharon, it was good
to see you, girl.

09:17.725 --> 09:19.359
Yeah. Sorry, Sharon.

09:19.392 --> 09:21.394
